## ğŸš€ What is Contribcast?

`contribcast` is a Python CLI tool that helps developers:

- Forecast and visualize their GitHub contributions ğŸ“Š  
- Get weekly reflection and motivational insights from AI ğŸ§   
- Discover trending beginner-friendly issues tailored to your stack ğŸ”  
- Automatically draft and submit PRs to practice contributing ğŸ’»  
- Schedule Slack reminders and generate dynamic README.md files ğŸ“  
- Empower both beginner and advanced developers to stay consistent

Whether you're new to open source or a seasoned contributor, Contribcast keeps your contribution game strong, organized, and automated.

