## ğŸ—“ï¸ Optional: Schedule Weekly Suggestions

Run once (e.g. with cron or `tmux`):

```bash
python contribcast/scheduler.py
```

This sends weekly issue suggestions to your Slack every Monday at 09:00 AM.

